10 REM OTF Slideshow Demo
20 REM This demo shows various images using On-the-Fly mode.
30 MODE &47: REM OTF 320x240x64, with 40x30 Text Area
40 CLS: VDU 23,1,0;0;0;0;
50 FDFLT%=&000F: FHIDE%=&000E
60 OTF%=&1E17
70 REM -- Load bitmaps and show each one
76 FOR ID%=101 TO 116
80 READ filename$
82 PRINT "Loading ";filename$
84 VDU OTF%;120,ID%;0;FHIDE%;320;240;1: REM Use PSRAM
90 infile=OPENIN filename$
100 IF infile=0 THEN END
110 FOR Y%=0 TO 239
120 VDU OTF%;132,ID%;0;Y%;320;
130 FOR X%=0 TO 319
140  temp%=BGET#infile
150  VDU temp%+&C0
160 NEXT X%
170 NEXT Y%
180 CLOSE#infile
190 VDU OTF%;4,ID%;
200 NEXT ID%
205 VDU OTF%;3,1;: REM Delete text area
205 REM -- Cycle through loaded bitmaps
210 FOR ID%=101 TO 116
211 VDU OTF%;0,ID%;FDFLT%;
212 START=TIME
213 IF TIME-START<50 THEN GOTO 213
214 VDU OTF%;0,ID%;FHIDE%;
227 NEXT ID%
228 GOTO 210
